  "lyrics": "[Music] Next time you see me a bit different I may be surprised with the smile A bit more effort visit In clips with a big moon still Next time I swear I'll have that money Each bill will be crispy Freshly printed in Turin County And we'll solve that I own You will be destroyed as a scale I can tell You think you know me well ► ► Next time you live, a long talk About pollinating you soon in your bones By the time we return from alone You'll be low still though Next time I'll bring you sources And a finally each one The next time you see a poor person You bleed. Sure you must lose skin. I know I will ► ► ►",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 12,
      "text": "[Music]",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 23.5,
      "text": "Next time you see me a bit different I may be surprised with the smile",
      "start": 11.5
    },
    {
      "end": 35,
      "text": "A bit more effort visit In clips with a big moon still",
      "start": 23
    },
    {
      "end": 46.5,
      "text": "Next time I swear I'll have that money Each bill will be crispy",
      "start": 34.5
    },
    {
      "end": 58,
      "text": "Freshly printed in Turin County And we'll solve that I own",
      "start": 46
    },
    {
      "end": 69.5,
      "text": "You will be destroyed as a scale I can tell",
      "start": 57.5
    },
    {
      "end": 81,
      "text": "You think you know me well",
      "start": 69
    },
    {
      "end": 92.5,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 80.5
    },
    {
      "end": 104,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 92
    },
    {
      "end": 115.5,
      "text": "Next time you live, a long talk About pollinating you soon in your bones",
      "start": 103.5
    },
    {
      "end": 127,
      "text": "By the time we return from alone You'll be low still though",
      "start": 115
    },
    {
      "end": 138.5,
      "text": "Next time I'll bring you sources And a finally each one",
      "start": 126.5
    },
    {
      "end": 150,
      "text": "The next time you see a poor person",
      "start": 138
    },
    {
      "end": 161.5,
      "text": "You bleed. Sure you must lose skin.",
      "start": 149.5
    },
    {
      "end": 173,
      "text": "I know I will",
      "start": 161
    },
    {
      "end": 184.5,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 172.5
    },
    {
      "end": 196,
      "text": "►",
      "start": 184
    },
    {
